						               													<description>Ahead of you lay a fiercely independent land of swamps, scattered village communities and hard-eyed people fighting for survival, as the fierce dusklings mount raid after raid.&amp;#10;It will take determination to win through here.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Welcome to a new campaign expansion for Five Leagues From the Borderlands, offering a brand new realm to explore. In a wet and rainy land, the feared dusklings are raiding ever more aggressively, leading to the call for heroes to hold the lines.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Marches is a pre-configured campaign featuring 5 villages, each with their own special circumstance and threat levels. The battles here will put you against the Dusklings: Orc-like raiders terrorizing civilization.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The feature list includes:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Simple rules for special terrain conditions and campaign adjustments, reflecting the unique circumstances of the Marches.&amp;#10;     Additional special rules for fighting the Duskling threat.&amp;#10;     Each of the 5 villages you have to clear has a special rule applicable to it.&amp;#10;     A new travel table for adventures in the Marches.&amp;#10;     A modified Monster table, including the new Swamp Lurker.&amp;#10;     10 Unique encounters to experience. &amp;#10;     3 new locations to visit.&amp;#10;     A 6 step quest adding new challenges and rewards as you play.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Distant Marches is intended to be played with Five Leagues From the Borderlands 2nd edition version 1.03 or newer, though any version from 1.0 Marmoset should work fine.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
